 to get a handle to a query that has already been analyzed.
 Query run-time execution is then a matter of finding the vertex 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset


\family sans
\size footnotesize
\emph on
sales
\family default
\size default
\emph default

\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

