\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ R\right\} $
\end_inset

 of employees in 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset


\family sans
\size footnotesize
\emph on
sales
\family default
\size default
\emph default

\begin_inset Quotes erd
