\family sans
\size footnotesize
(Lambda (Variable $x) (Plus (Variable $x) (Number 2)))
\family default
\size default
'.
 This expression is obviously equivalent to 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda y.\left(y+2\right)$
\end_inset

 or '
\family sans
\size footnotesize
(Lambda (Variable $y) (Plus (Variable $y) (Number 2)))
\family default
\size default
'.
